    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
