      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add the <strong>chicken stock</strong> and <strong>ground almonds</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 5-6 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once done, stir in your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and cook for a further 1 min or until it's warmed through – this is your<strong> mild chicken breast korma</strong></p>",
